  "short_description": "Brawlers of Duality is a top-down arena fighter where damaging enemies launches them further, launch enemies out of the arena to defeat them. Battle in 1v1, 2v2, and a FFA mode where you defeat enemies to power up and take on other players. BoD is still under development",
