  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Knock back and knock out opponents</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight and launch your opponents around the arena. As you deal damage your opponents will get knocked back further and faster. Position yourself and aim your attacks to knock your opponents out of the ring. In the Bash game mode knock opponents into parts of the environment that have been corrupted by magic to knock them out. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/6e38bda5017008cab302bd7bab959164.poster.avif?t=1763848176\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/6e38bda5017008cab302bd7bab959164.webm?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/6e38bda5017008cab302bd7bab959164.mp4?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Tag team fighting</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a team of three characters that can be swapped to mid combo. Strategically create a team, pick characters that cover each others weaknesses, or play to each others strengths.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/aa4bd4230cf849548a3393383fd9db5a.poster.avif?t=1763848176\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/aa4bd4230cf849548a3393383fd9db5a.webm?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/aa4bd4230cf849548a3393383fd9db5a.mp4?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Brawl and Bash</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against 3 other players and many enemies to get loot that powers you up in this unique 4 player free-for-all throughout the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/2126283e6468e229a158a0ac2d9729fd.poster.avif?t=1763848176\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/2126283e6468e229a158a0ac2d9729fd.webm?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/2126283e6468e229a158a0ac2d9729fd.mp4?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Try out the demo!</strong><br>This is my first game and I'm still working on it. Try the demo, I want to let as many people try it as possible, but if you enjoy it feel free to support the game by purchasing! The demo gives you access to 3 characters and lets you try the game before you buy. Please give it a try and if you have any issues or feedback contact us! I'm still working on the game and fixing bugs, but people wanted a way to support the development so the game is available for purchase.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Knock back and knock out opponents</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight and launch your opponents around the arena. As you deal damage your opponents will get knocked back further and faster. Position yourself and aim your attacks to knock your opponents out of the ring. In the Bash game mode knock opponents into parts of the environment that have been corrupted by magic to knock them out. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/6e38bda5017008cab302bd7bab959164.poster.avif?t=1763848176\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/6e38bda5017008cab302bd7bab959164.webm?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/6e38bda5017008cab302bd7bab959164.mp4?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Tag team fighting</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a team of three characters that can be swapped to mid combo. Strategically create a team, pick characters that cover each others weaknesses, or play to each others strengths.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/aa4bd4230cf849548a3393383fd9db5a.poster.avif?t=1763848176\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/aa4bd4230cf849548a3393383fd9db5a.webm?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/aa4bd4230cf849548a3393383fd9db5a.mp4?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Brawl and Bash</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against 3 other players and many enemies to get loot that powers you up in this unique 4 player free-for-all throughout the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/2126283e6468e229a158a0ac2d9729fd.poster.avif?t=1763848176\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/2126283e6468e229a158a0ac2d9729fd.webm?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990990/extras/2126283e6468e229a158a0ac2d9729fd.mp4?t=1763848176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Try out the demo!</strong><br>This is my first game and I'm still working on it. Try the demo, I want to let as many people try it as possible, but if you enjoy it feel free to support the game by purchasing! The demo gives you access to 3 characters and lets you try the game before you buy. Please give it a try and if you have any issues or feedback contact us! I'm still working on the game and fixing bugs, but people wanted a way to support the development so the game is available for purchase.</p>",
